==English==

===Noun ===

'''call sign'''

# {{military}} Any combination of characters or pronounceable words, which identifies a communication facility, a [[command]], an [[authority]], an [[activity]], or a [[unit]]; used primarily for [[establishing]] and [[maintaining]] [[communications]]. Also called [[CS]].
# (''broadcasting'') A combination of letters used to identify a radio or television station.

